msgctxt "2704"
msgid "Nakano"
msgstr "Nakano"

msgctxt "2708"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "2712"
msgid "Saejima"
msgstr "Saejima"

msgctxt "2716"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "72_Nakano"
msgid "Still looking for the Florist?"
msgstr "¿Sigues buscando al Florista?"

msgctxt "84_Nakano"
msgid "I heard his hideout's through the bathroom at West Park."
msgstr "Escuché que al fondo del Parque Oeste\r\n"
"puedes llegar al Florista."

msgctxt "96_Nakano"
msgid "You're searching for the city's biggest info dealer－\r\n"
"the Florist, right?"
msgstr "¿Estás buscando al legendario informante?\r\n"
"¿El Florista de Sai, verdad?"

msgctxt "108_Saejima"
msgid "If that's his name."
msgstr "¿Ese es su nombre?"

msgctxt "120_Nakano"
msgid "That's what his clients call him, anyway. It's because\r\n"
"the info he sells gets delivered inside flower bouquets."
msgstr "Bueno, es más como un apodo.\r\n"
"La historia es que entregaba información a sus clientes junto con flores."

msgctxt "132_Saejima"
msgid "Sounds real romantic. So how's a guy meet this Florist?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿cómo puedo encontrarme con ese tal florista?\r\n"
"¿Dónde está?"

msgctxt "144_Nakano"
msgid "The thing is, no one really knows, what with all the crazy\r\n"
"stuff that's happened around here over the past few years."
msgstr "Bueno, desde hace unos años no se sabe su paradero.\r\n"
"Eso después de todos los problemas de los años anteriores"

msgctxt "156_Nakano"
msgid "Seems like every time a major crisis hits the city,\r\n"
"he uproots his headquarters and relocates."
msgstr "Se dice que ha estado cambiando de lugar\r\n"
"para evitar problemas."

msgctxt "168_Saejima"
msgid "Any idea where he's planted himself now?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿no sabes dónde está ahora?\r\n"
"¿No hay ninguna pista de su paradero?"

msgctxt "180_Nakano"
msgid "Don't know for sure, but there is a rumor going around."
msgstr "Bueno, se me ocurre un lugar."

msgctxt "192_Saejima"
msgid "I'm listenin'."
msgstr "¿Cuál?"

msgctxt "204_Nakano"
msgid "I heard you can get to his hideout through the back\r\n"
"of the public restroom at West Park."
msgstr "En los baños del Parque Oeste. Escuché que por\r\n"
"allí puedes llegar al Florista."

msgctxt "216_Saejima"
msgid "Ya mean the john at the north end of town?"
msgstr "¿El Parque Oeste... al norte de Kamurocho, verdad?"

msgctxt "228_Nakano"
msgid "That's the one. I'd start there at West Park if I were you."
msgstr "Ese mismo. Si fuera tú, empezaría por allí."

msgctxt "240_Saejima"
msgid "Alright, thanks."
msgstr "Muy bien, gracias."

